    Combines Spearman dissimilarity and Euclidean distance in parallel

    CombinedPar.Rd

    This function uses parallel computing to calculate both Spearman dissimilarity and Euclidean distance, combines them, and performs t-SNE.

    CombinedPar(ptmtable.df, ptmtable)

    Arguments

    ptmtable.df

    A data frame containing numeric data.

    ptmtable

    A dataset for post-translational modifications.

    Value

    A matrix containing t-SNE coordinates (3D).

    Examples

    CombinedPar(ptmtable.df, ptmtable)
